{"kanda":6,"sarga":128,"description":"","verses":[{"v":1,"dev":"अयोध्यांतुसमालोक्यचिन्तयामासराघवः ।प्रियकामःप्रियंरामस्ततस्त्वरितविक्रमः","trans":"There upon Raghava who was quick in exhibiting his prowess started thinking with his friends looking at Ayodhya (from Pushpaka).","words":[{"d":"ततः","m":"thereupon"},{"d":"राघवः","m":"Raghava"},{"d":"त्वरितविक्रमः","m":"quick in exhibiting prowess"},{"d":"रामः","m":"Rama"},{"d":"अयोध्याम्","m":"Ayodhya"},{"d":"समालोक्य","m":"with friends प्रियकामः wished"},{"d":"प्रियम्","m":"dear"},{"d":"चिन्तयामास","m":"started thinking"}]},{"v":2,"dev":"चिन्तयित्वाततोदृष्टिंवानरेषुन्यपातयत् ।उवाचधीमांस्तेजस्वीहनूमन्तंप्लवङ्गमम्","trans":"Then wise and energetic Rama, thinking, casting his attention on the Vanaras, spoke to Hanuman.","words":[{"d":"ततः","m":"then"},{"d":"धीमान्","m":"wise"},{"d":"तेजस्वी","m":"energetic"},{"d":"चिन्तयित्वा","m":"thinking"},{"d":"वानरेषु","m":"to Vanaras"},{"d":"दृष्टिम्","m":"mind"},{"d":"न्यपातयत्","m":"casting his attention"},{"d":"प्लवङ्गमम्","m":"monkeys"},{"d":"हनूमन्तम्","m":"Hanumantha"},{"d":"उवाच","m":"spoke"}]},{"v":3,"dev":"अयोध्यांत्वरितोगत्वाशीघ्रंप्लवगसत्तम ।जानीहिकछचित्कुशलीजनोनृपतिमन्दिरे","trans":"\"Chief of monkeys! Going quickly to the king's mansion in Ayodhya try to find out about the wellbeing of the people.\"","words":[{"d":"प्लवगसत्तम","m":"chief of monkeys"},{"d":"त्वरितः","m":"going quickly"},{"d":"अयोध्याम्","m":"Ayodhya"},{"d":"शीघ्रम्","m":"hastily"},{"d":"गत्वा","m":"going"},{"d":"नृपतिमन्दिरे","m":"king's mansion"},{"d":"जनः","m":"people"},{"d":"कुशलीकचचित्","m":"wellbeing"},{"d":"जानीहि","m":"try to know"}]},{"v":4,"dev":"शृङ्गबेरिपुरंप्राप्यगुहंगहनगोचरम् ।निषादाधिपतिंब्रूहिकुशलंवचनान्मम","trans":"\"Go to Sringaberipuram which is seen from the sky, meet Guha the leader of Nishadas and tell him of my inquiry and wellbeing.\"","words":[{"d":"शृङ्गबेरिपुरम्","m":"Sringaberipuram"},{"d":"गत्वा","m":"going"},{"d":"गहनगोचरम्","m":"seen from the sky"},{"d":"निषादाधिपतिम्","m":"