":"Hanuman"},{"d":"त्वरितः","m":"speedily"},{"d":"मानुषंरूपम्","m":"human form"},{"d":"धारयन्","m":"taking"},{"d":"अयोध्याम्","m":"to Ayodhya"},{"d":"ययौ","m":"went"}]},{"v":20,"dev":"अतोत्पपातवेगेनहनूमान्मारुतात्मजः ।गरुत्मानिववेगेनजिघृक्षन्पन्नगोत्तमम्","trans":"Then Hanuman rose up just like Garuda who goes at great speed to vanquish the best of serpents.","words":[{"d":"अथ","m":"and then"},{"d":"मारुतात्मजंहनूमान्","m":"Hanuman, the son of Maruti"},{"d":"पन्नगोत्तमम्","m":"the best of serpents"},{"d":"वेगेन","m":"at great speed"},{"d":"जिघृक्षन्","m":"vanquish"},{"d":"गरुत्मानिव","m":"like Garuda"},{"d":"वेगेन","m":"speedily"},{"d":"उत्पपात","m":"rose"}]},{"v":21,"dev":"लङ्घयित्वापितृपथंविहगेन्द्रालयंशुभम् ।गङ्गायमुनयोर्भीमंसमतीत्यसमागमम् शृङ्गबेरपुरंप्राप्यगुहमासाद्यवीर्यवान् ।स वाचाशुभयाहृष्टोहनुमानिदमब्रवीत्","trans":"Valiant Hanuman, flying through the course of the birds, through the auspicious path of the wind god, leaping across Ganga and Yamuna, reached Sringaberipuram, saw Guha, rejoiced and thus spoke charming words.","words":[{"d":"वीर्यवान्","m":"valiant"},{"d":"सःहनुमान्","m":"that Hanuman"},{"d":"विहगेन्द्रालयम्","m":"the course of the birds"},{"d":"शुभम्","m":"auspicious"},{"d":"पितृपथम्","m":"path of wind god"},{"d":"लङ्घयित्वा","m":"leaping"},{"d":"गङ्गायमुनयोः","m":"Ganga and Yamuna"},{"d":"भीमम्","m":"frightening"},{"d":"समागमम्","m":"confluence"},{"d":"समतीत्य","m":"reaching"},{"d":"शृङ्गबेरिपुरम्","m":"Sringaberipuram"},{"d":"प्राप्य","m":"attaining"},{"d":"गुहम्","m":"Guha"},{"d":"आसाद्य","m":"seeing"},{"d":"हृष्टः","m":"joyful"},{"d":"शुभया","m":"charming"},{"d":"वाचा","m":"words"},{"d":"इदम्","m":"thus"},{"d":"अब्रवीत्","m":"spoke"}]},{"v":22,"dev":"लङ्घयित्वापितृपथंविहगेन्द्रालयंशुभम् ।गङ्गायमुनयोर्भीमंसमतीत्यसमागमम् शृङ्गबेरपुरंप्राप्यगुहमासाद्यवीर्यवान् ।स वाचाशुभयाहृष्टोहनुमानिदमब्रवीत्","trans":"Valiant Hanuman, flying through the course of the birds, through the auspicious path of the wind god, leaping across Ganga and Yamuna, reached Sringaberipuram, saw Guha, rejoiced and thus spoke charming words.","words":[{"d":"वीर्यवान्","m":"valiant"},{"d":"सःहनुमान्","m":"that Hanuman"},{"d":"विहगेन्द्रालयम्","m":"the course of the birds"},{"d":"शुभम्","m":"auspicious"},{"d":"पितृपथम्","m":"path of wind god"},{"d":"लङ्घयित्वा","m":"leaping"},{"d":"गङ्गायमुनयोः","m":"Ganga and Yamuna"},{"d":"भीमम्","m":"frightening"},{"d":"समागमम्","m":"confluence"},{"d":"समतीत्य","m":"reaching"},{"d":"शृङ्गबेरिपुरम्","m":"Sringaberipuram"},{"d":"प्राप्य","m":"attaining"},{"d":"गुहम्","m":"Guha"},{"d":"आसाद्य","m":"seeing"},{"d":"हृष्टः","m":"joyful"},{"d":"शुभया","m":"charming"},{"d":"वाचा","m":"words"},{"d":"इदम्","m":"thus"},{"d":"अब्रवीत्","m":"spoke"}]},{"v":23,"dev":"सखातुतवकाकुत्स्थोरामस्सत्यपराक्रमः ।ससीतस्सहसौमित्रिस्सत्वांकुशलमब्रवीत्","trans":"\"Your friend Rama, truly valiant one, with his wife Sita, with Lakshmana conveys his welfare to you.\"","words":[{"d":"तव","m":"your"},{"d":"सखा","m":"friend"},{"d":"काकुत्स्थ:","m":"Kakuthsa"},{"d":"सत्यपराक्रमः","m":"truly valiant"},{"d":"ससीतः","m":"with Sita"},{"d":"सहसौमित्रिः","m":"with Saumithri"},{"d":"सःरामः","m":"he, Rama"},{"d":"त्वाम्","m":"you"},{"d":"कुशलम्","m":"welfare"},{"d":"अब्रवीत्","m":"said"}]},{"v":24,"dev":"पञ्चमीमद्यरजनीमुषित्वावचनान्मुनेः ।भरद्वाजाभ्यनुज्ञातंद्रक्ष्यस्यद्यैवराघवम्","trans":"\"Tomorrow that is the fifth lunar day, after spending the night at sage Bharadwaja's hermitage Raghava will see you.\"","words":[{"d":"अद्य","m":"today"},{"d":"मुनेः","m":"sage"},{"d":"वचनात्","m":"by the words"},{"d":"पञ्चमीम्","m":"fifth"},{"d":"रजनीम्","m":"night"},{"d":"उषित्वा","m":"night"},{"d":"भरद्वाजाभ्यनुज्ञातम्","m":"with the permission of Bharadvaja"},{"d":"राघवम्","m":"Raghava"},{"d":"अद्यैव","m":"morning"},{"d":"द्रक्ष्यसि","m":"you will see"}]},{"v":25,"dev":"एवमुक्त्वामहातेजास्सम्प्रहृष्टतनूरुहः ।उत्पपातमहावेगाद्वेगवान्विचारयन्","trans":"Highly energetic Hanuman, was thrilled, overcome with happiness (that he was able to communicate to Guha) and unmindful of the fatigue, being endowed with speed and swift movement, went up.","words":[{"d":"महातेजाः","m":"highly energetic"},{"d":"सम्प्रहृष्टतनूरुहः","m":"thrilled overcome by happiness"},{"d":"वेगवान्","m":"endowed with speed"},{"d":"अविचारयन्","m":"not caring for the fatigue"},{"d":"महावेगात्","m":"swift moving"},{"d":"उत्पपात","m":"went up"}]},{"v":26,"dev":"सोऽपश्यद्रामतीर्थं च नदींवालुकिनींतथा ।वरूथींगोमतींचैवभीमंशालवनंतथा प्रजाश्चबहुसाहस्रीःस्फीतान्जनपदानपि ।","trans":"He saw waters associated with Parasurama, and rivers Valukini, Varuthini, and Gomathi so also fearful woods of Sala trees and thousands of people, numerous kingdoms on the way.","words":[{"d":"सः","m":"he"},{"d":"वालुकिनींनदीम्","m":"Valukini"},{"d":"वरूथीम्","m":"Varuthimi"},{"d":"गोमतींचैव","m":"Gomathi"},{"d":"तथा","m":"so also"},{"d":"भीमम्","m":"fearful"},{"d":"शालवनम्","m":"Sal woods"},{"d":"बहुसाहस्रीः","m":"many thousands"},{"d":"प्रजाश्च","m":"people"},{"d":"स्फीतान्","m":"numerous"},{"d":"जनपदानपि","m":"kingdoms"},{"d":"अपश्यत्","m":"saw"}]},{"v":27,"dev":"सःगत्वादूरमध्वानंत्वरितःकपिकुञ्जरः आससादद्रुमान् फुल्लान्नन्दिग्रामसमीपगान् ।स्त्रीभिस्सपुत्रैर्वृद्धैश्चरममाणैःस्वलङ्कृतैः ।सुराधिपस्योपवनेयथाचैत्ररथेद्रुमान्","trans":"Speeding on the journey for long distance Hanuman, the elephant among the monkeys saw women, their sons, grand sons and the old, well decorated, sporting in the gardens which were like the gardens of Indra and the gardens of Chaitraratha of Kubera with trees and close to Nandigrama, he saw trees full of blossoms.","words":[{"d":"सः","m":"he"},{"d":"कपिकुञ्जरः","m":"elephant among monkeys"},{"d":"त्वरितः","m":"soon"},{"d":"दूरम्","m":"distance"},{"d":"अध्वानम्","m":"speeding on the journey"},{"d":"गत्वा","m":"going"},{"d":"स्त्रीभिः","m":"women"},{"d":"सपुत्रैः","m":"their sons"},{"d":"स्वलङ्कृतैः","m":"well decorated"},{"d":"रममाणैः","m":"sporting"},{"d":"वृद्धैश्चज","m":"old people"},{"d":"सुराधिपस्य","m":"like that of Indra"},{"d":"उपवने","m":"gardens"},{"d":"चैत्ररथे","m":"Chaitraratha"},{"d":"द्रुमान्यथा","m":"trees"},{"d":"नन्दिग्रामसमीपगान्","m":"close by Nandigrama"},{"d":"फुल्लान्","m":"blossoms"},{"d":"द्रुमान्","m":"trees"},{"d":"आससाद","m":"reached"}]},{"v":28,"dev":"सःगत्वादूरमध्वानंत्वरितःकपिकुञ्जरः आससादद्रुमान् फुल्लान्नन्दिग्रामसमीपगान् ।स्त्रीभिस्सपुत्रैर्वृद्धैश्चरममाणैःस्वलङ्कृतैः ।सुराधिपस्योपवनेयथाचैत्ररथेद्रुमान्","trans":"Speeding on the journey for long distance Hanuman, the elephant among the monkeys saw women, their sons, grand sons and the old, well decorated, sporting in the gardens which were like the gardens of Indra and the gardens of Chaitraratha of Kubera with trees and close to Nandigrama, he saw trees full of blossoms.","words":[{"d":"सः","m":"he"},{"d":"कपिकुञ्जरः","m":"elephant among monkeys"},{"d":"त्वरितः","m":"soon"},{"d":"दूरम्","m":"distance"},{"d":"अध्वानम्","m":"speeding on the journey"},{"d":"गत्वा","m":"going"},{"d":"स्त्रीभिः","m":"women"},{"d":"सपुत्रैः","m":"their sons"},{"d":"स्वलङ्कृतैः","m":"well decorated"},{"d":"रममाणैः","m":"sporting"},{"d":"वृद्धैश्चज","m":"old people"},{"d":"सुराधिपस्य","m":"like that of Indra"},{"d":"उपवने","m":"gardens"},{"d":"चैत्ररथे","m":"Chaitraratha"},{"d":"द्रुमान्यथा","m":"trees"},{"d":"नन्दिग्रामसमीपगान्","m":"close by Nandigrama"},{"d":"फुल्लान्","m":"blossoms"},{"d":"द्रुमान्","m":"trees"},{"d":"आससाद","m":"reached"}]},{"v":29,"dev":"क्रोशमात्रेत्वयोध्यायाचशीरकृष्णाजिनम्बरम् ददर्शभरतंदीनंकृशमाश्रमवासिनम् ।जटिलंमलदिग्धाङ्गंभ्रातृव्यसनकर्शितम् ।।6.128.30 ।फलमूलाशिनंदान्तंतापसंधर्मचारिणम् ।समुन्नतजटाभारंवल्कलाजिनवाससम् नियतंभावितात्मानंब्रह्मर्षिसमतेजसम् ।पादुकेतेपुरस्कृत्यप्रशासन्तंवसुन्धराम् ।।6.128.32 ।चातुर्वर्णस्यलोकस्यत्रातारंमहतोभयात् ।उपस्थितममात्यैश्चशुचिभिश्चपुरोहितैः बलमुख्यैश्चयुक्तैश्चकाषायाम्बरदारिभिः ।","trans":"' At a distance of two miles from Ayodhya, Hanuman saw Bharata living in a hermitage wearing black skin of antelope, emaciated, piteous, not clean, without any cleaning of the body, affected by the separation from brother living on fruits and roots, subdued practicing austerities, following righteous practices disciplined, soul purified by meditation, like Brahmarshi in brilliance, placing your sandals on ground ruling the earth, all the four divisions free from fear on all sides, protecting the upright, ministers, priests, united with chiefs of army stood there' (reported Hanuman).","words":[{"d":"अयोध्यायाः","m":"in Ayodhya"},{"d":"क्रोशमात्रे","m":"two miles distance"},{"d":"चीरकृष्णाजिनाम्बरम्","m":"wearing the skin of antelope"},{"d":"दीनम्","m":"piteously"},{"d":"कृशम्","m":"emaciated"},{"d":"जटिलम्","m":"miserable"},{"d":"मलदिग्धाङ्गम्","m":"dirty without any cleaning"},{"d":"भ्रातृव्यसनकर्शितम्","m":"afflicted by the separation of the brother"},{"d":"फलमूलशिनम्","m":"living on fruits and roots"},{"d":"दान्तम्","m":"subdued"},{"d":"तापसम्","m":"practicing austerities"},{"d":"धर्मचारिणम्","m":"following righteous practices"},{"d":"समुन्नतजटाभारम्","m":"very high matted hair"},{"d":"वल्कलाजिनवाससम्","m":"wearing upper part with bark"},{"d":"नियतम्","m":"disciplined"},{"d":"भावितात्मानम्","m":"whose soul is purified by meditation"},{"d":"ब्रह्मर्षिसमतेजसम्","m":"like Brahmarshi in brilliance"},{"d":"ते","m":"your"},{"d":"पादुके","m":"sandals"},{"d":"पुरस्कृत्य","m":"placing"},{"d":"वसुन्धराम्","m":"on the ground"},{"d":"प्रशासन्तम्","m":"ruling"},{"d":"चातुर्वर्ण्यस्य","m":"all the four divisions"},{"d":"लोकस्य","m":"of the world"},{"d":"भयात्","m":"from fear"},{"d":"त्रातारम्","m":"protecting"},{"d":"शुचिभिः","m":"upright"},{"d":"अमात्यैश्च","m":"ministers"},{"d":"पुरोहितैः","m":"priests"},{"d":"युक्तै:","m":"united with"},{"d":"बलमुख्यैश्च","m":"chiefs of army"},{"d":"उपस्थितम्","m":"stood"},{"d":"आश्रमवासिनम्","m":"living in the hermitage"},{"d":"भरतम्","m":"Bharata"},{"d":"ददर्श","m":"saw"}]},{"v":30,"dev":"क्रोशमात्रेत्वयोध्यायाचशीरकृष्णाजिनम्बरम् ददर्शभरतंदीनंकृशमाश्रमवासिनम् ।जटिलंमलदिग्धाङ्गंभ्रातृव्यसनकर्शितम् ।।6.128.30 ।फलमूलाशिनंदान्तंतापसंधर्मचारिणम् ।समुन